Prerequisites (C part)
 GCC compiler(version 9 or later)
 make (optional)
 Standard C Libraries(stdio,stdlib,type,etc)
 

Step by step  building instructions ( C part)
    Navigate to the source  directory:
         sd c_simulator/
    Compile the program :
         gcc -o simulator main.c scheduler .c-I'm

    Run the simulator:
      ./simulator. input 

Prerequisites (Python part)
   python version 3.8 or later
   no external libraries required

Building python instructions 
  Navigate to python directory:
     cd python_ smulator/
  Run the script:
     python3 smulator.py input.text

